        							<img src="/web/20120724004343im_/http://www.wonderfulwaterloo.com/image.php?s=c1a52c67f90c6bff91e2f4520cbde799&amp;u=2&amp;dateline=1320406213" alt="UrbanWaterloo's Avatar" style="max-height: 45px" />
        						
