                                        <span class="nodecontrols" style="font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal;">
                                                
                                                        <a name="post294" href="/web/20120724004343/http://www.wonderfulwaterloo.com/showthread.php?t=66&amp;s=c1a52c67f90c6bff91e2f4520cbde799&amp;p=294#post294" class="postcounter">#4</a><a id="postcount294" name="4"></a>
                                                
                                                
                                                
